—ЩParchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/from_tsv.mdЩ@488a098795787cbad85df7fc205acef69248cba49a7765014a49db1bf23b7f90Їtitle: from tsv‘ҐFlagsЪ,``--comment, -c {string}``
: A comment character to ignore lines starting with it.
``--quote, -q {string}``
: A quote character to ignore separators in strings, defaults to '"'.
``--escape, -e {string}``
: An escape character for strings containing the quote character.
``--noheaders, -n``
: Don't treat the first row as column names.
``--flexible``
: Allow the number of fields in records to be variable.
``--no-infer``
: No field type inferencing.
``--trim, -t {string}``
: Drop leading and trailing whitespaces around headers names and/or field values.
’ђђЪXTitle: title: from tsv
Path: Flags
Content:
``--comment, -c {string}``
: A comment character to ignore lines starting with it.
``--quote, -q {string}``
: A quote character to ignore separators in strings, defaults to '"'.
``--escape, -e {string}``
: An escape character for strings containing the quote character.
``--noheaders, -n``
: Don't treat the first row as column names.
``--flexible``
: Allow the number of fields in records to be variable.
``--no-infer``
: No field type inferencing.
``--trim, -t {string}``
: Drop leading and trailing whitespaces around headers names and/or field values.
